        public List<SuggestionItem> lookupCompound(String phrase,
                                           double maxEditDistance)
                                    throws SpellCheckException
        supports compound aware automatic spelling correction of multi-word input strings with three cases 1. mistakenly inserted space into a correct word led to two incorrect terms 2. mistakenly omitted space between two correct words led to one incorrect combined term 3. multiple independent input terms with/without spelling errors Find suggested spellings for a multi-word input string (supports word splitting/merging).
